title: Braza Flash Tape - Double Sided Clear Adhesive Clothing, Fabric and Body Tape, (4) 20ft Rolls
description: Double-sided tape in a dispenser – It's one of our best selling products and sets the industry standard.  Flash Tape is a Registered Trademark.   The list of uses keeps growing! Secure: Deep plunge clothing, open-sided dresses, wrap-style tops, gaps between buttons, tube tops and halters, cuffs, scarfs, socks and jewelry, open hems, bra straps, shoulder pads and more. It also helps secure Face Masks. Now safe for crafts, photo albums and archiving important documents. Fumble-free dispenser has convenient ‘crack-n-peel’ liner for easy application. Water resistant.
